["```\r\n<project  xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" \r\nxsi:schemaLocation=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd\">\r\n    <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>\r\n    <groupId>com.baeldung.maven.plugin</groupId>\r\n    <artifactId>host-maven-repo-example</artifactId>\r\n    <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>\r\n    <build>\r\n        <pluginManagement>\r\n            <plugins>\r\n                <plugin>\r\n                    <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>\r\n                    <artifactId>maven-compiler-plugin</artifactId>\r\n                    <configuration>\r\n                        <source>1.8</source>\r\n                        <target>1.8</target>\r\n                    </configuration>\r\n                </plugin>\r\n            </plugins>\r\n        </pluginManagement>\r\n    </build>\r\n<project>\r\n```","```\r\n<distributionManagement> \r\n    <repository>\r\n        <id>internal.repo</id> \r\n        <name>Temporary Staging Repository</name> \r\n        <url>file://${project.build.directory}/mvn-artifact</url> \r\n    </repository> \r\n</distributionManagement> \r\n```","```\r\n<plugin>\r\n    <artifactId>maven-deploy-plugin</artifactId>\r\n    <version>2.8.2</version>\r\n    <configuration>\r\n        <altDeploymentRepository>\r\n            internal.repo::default::file://${project.build.directory}/mvn-artifact\r\n        </altDeploymentRepository>\r\n    </configuration>\r\n</plugin>\r\n```","```\r\n<plugin>\r\n    <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>\r\n    <artifactId>maven-source-plugin</artifactId>\r\n    <version>3.1.0</version>\r\n    <executions>\r\n        <execution>\r\n            <id>attach-sources</id>\r\n                <goals>\r\n                    <goal>jar</goal>\r\n                </goals>\r\n        </execution>\r\n    </executions>\r\n</plugin>\r\n```","```\r\n<settings>\r\n    <servers>\r\n        <server>\r\n            <id>github</id>\r\n            <username>your Github username</username>\r\n            <password>your Github password</password>\r\n        </server>\r\n    </servers>\r\n</settings>\r\n```","```\r\n<settings>\r\n    <servers> \r\n        <server>\r\n            <id>github</id>\r\n            <password>YOUR GitHub OAUTH-TOKEN</password>\r\n        </server>\r\n    </servers>\r\n</settings>\r\n```","```\r\n<plugin>\r\n    <groupId>com.github.github</groupId>\r\n    <artifactId>site-maven-plugin</artifactId>\r\n    <version>0.12</version>\r\n    <configuration>\r\n        <message>Maven artifacts for ${project.version}</message>\r\n        <noJekyll>true</noJekyll>\r\n        <outputDirectory>${project.build.directory}</outputDirectory>\r\n        <branch>refs/heads/${branch-name}</branch>\r\n        <includes>\r\n            <include>**/*</include>\r\n        </includes>\r\n        <merge>true</merge>\r\n        <repositoryName>${repository-name}</repositoryName>\r\n        <repositoryOwner>${repository-owner}</repositoryOwner>\r\n        <server>github</server>\r\n    </configuration>\r\n    <executions>\r\n        <execution>\r\n            <goals>\r\n                <goal>site</goal>\r\n            </goals>\r\n            <phase>deploy</phase>\r\n        </execution>\r\n    </executions>\r\n</plugin>\r\n```"]